<br>
Only my 2cp<br>
<br>
How can a Open system be wrong? The closed system has no advantage over the public expept that it is a bit more time-consuming at the auctioning. But look at all these rules you want for closed bids; Rotating auctioneer, letting a person not loose more RPs than needed and so on. Please use a open system and let it be fair, simple, easy, and let it take a few minutes more. Otherwise noone will understand the system more than the ML and everyone will wonder what happened afterwards.<br>
<br>
I am though happy with the proposal that the RL may choose, and I hope someone soon chooses open bidding, so we all get a feeling of that system. <p>--------------------------<br>
